Package: rgsp
Type: Package
Title: Graph Signal Processing Toolkit in R (Port of PyGSP)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person(given = "Your", family = "Name", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Graph signal processing on graphs (construction, filters, spectral transforms,
    learning/optimization) ported from PyGSP 0.6.1 (EPFL LTS2, BSD-3-Clause; see
    inst/COPYRIGHTS). Core numerics implemented in C++ via RcppArmadillo with optional
    OpenMP acceleration.
